snippet.title: Cut the Rope 3 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The newest chapter in the legendary Cut the Rope franchise whisks you away into a vibrant and immersive world. The key to travelling is getting the restless Nibble Nom back to Om Nom, but how to do this? Level objects will help – if you think of a way to use them. Work it out 🧩 A great adventure awaits you 🎉

Find Cut the Rope 3 on Apple Arcade now
https://apple.co/ctr-3
